Quantitative Comparison Report
for Thunder Bay Art Gallery








Introduction

This report has been provided to you to help you compare your charity’s key financial performance indicators against 9 other charities in the Libraries, museums… category. The financial data used in this report comes from the 2015 copy of the T3010 charity tax return. As such, the accuracy of the data and all indicators in this report is dependent on the information provided to Canada Revenue Agency by all registered charities. Therefore if there are any data quality issues, then I do not assume any responsibility for them.

The 9 other charities selected as comparators to your charity were the closest to your charity in terms of receipted + non-receipted donation total. In each section of this report you will find a table and an adjacent graph that enable you to compare your charity against the 9 others in terms of a variety of financial performance indicators. The indicator will be described at the beginning of each section and results are ordered by the value of the indicator.
